<subSubSection box="[189,1249,1883,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,1415,2090]" box="[189,1249,1883,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,356,1884,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">Etymology:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meng &amp; Guo &amp; Zhang &amp; Kociolek &amp; Li" authorityYear="2022" box="[356,474,1883,1909]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Cymbellaceae" genus="Cymbopleura" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Cymbellales" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="deqinensis">
<emphasis box="[356,474,1883,1909]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">deqinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, refers to the 
<typeStatus box="[629,677,1884,1910]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">type</typeStatus>
locality from which the new species was obtained.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="235" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,1415,2090]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,321,1920,1946]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">Ecology:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meng &amp; Guo &amp; Zhang &amp; Kociolek &amp; Li" authorityYear="2022" box="[322,602,1919,1945]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Cymbellaceae" genus="Cymbopleura" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Cymbellales" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="deqinensis">
<emphasis box="[322,602,1919,1945]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">Cymbopleura deqinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from the surface sediments of an unnamed lake occurring at about 
<quantity box="[240,329,1956,1982]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.901" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" unit="m" value="4901.0">4901 m</quantity>
asl. At the 
<typeStatus box="[470,518,1956,1982]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">type</typeStatus>
locality, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meng &amp; Guo &amp; Zhang &amp; Kociolek &amp; Li" authorityYear="2022" box="[629,783,1955,1982]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Cymbellaceae" genus="Cymbopleura" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Cymbellales" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="deqinensis">
<emphasis box="[629,783,1955,1982]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">C. deqinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was uncommon (&lt;1% abundance); the related species in decreasing order of abundance were 
<taxonomicName authority="(Ehrenberg) Bukhtiyarova (1995: 418)" authorityName="Bukhtiyarova" authorityPageNumber="418" authorityYear="1995" baseAuthorityName="Ehrenberg" box="[550,1341,1991,2018]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Fragilariaceae" form="venter" genus="Staurosira" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fragilariales" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="form" species="construens">
<emphasis box="[550,796,1992,2018]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">Staurosira construens</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis box="[827,897,1992,2017]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="235">venter</emphasis>
(Ehrenberg) 
<bibRefCitation author="Bukhtiyarova, L. N." box="[1047,1341,1991,2018]" pageId="2" pageNumber="235" pagination="417 - 424" refId="ref4807" refString="Bukhtiyarova, L. N. (1995) Novye taksonomischeskie kombinatsii diatomovykh vodoroslei (Bacillariophyta). Algologia 5 (4): 417 - 424." type="journal article" year="1995">Bukhtiyarova (1995: 418)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
